plan.description: Test the functionality of searching for emails containing the 'meeting' keyword in the inbox of the email application.

subgoals.expected_outcome: The email application opens and displays the inbox.
subgoals.verification_criteria: Check if the inbox view is displayed with a list of emails.

subgoals.description: Locate the search bar within the inbox.
subgoals.target_element: Search bar at the top of the inbox
subgoals.expected_outcome: The search bar is visible and ready for input.
subgoals.verification_criteria: Verify that the search bar is active and can be interacted with.

subgoals.description: Input the keyword 'meeting' into the search bar.
subgoals.expected_outcome: The keyword 'meeting' is entered into the search bar.
subgoals.verification_criteria: Check that the search bar contains the text 'meeting'.

subgoals.description: Initiate the search for emails by tapping the search button.
subgoals.target_element: Search button next to the search bar
subgoals.expected_outcome: The application processes the search request and displays results.
subgoals.verification_criteria: Verify that the email results displayed contain emails with the keyword 'meeting'.

subgoals.description: Scroll through the search results to ensure all results can be viewed.
subgoals.expected_outcome: The user can scroll through all the displayed emails containing 'meeting'.
subgoals.verification_criteria: Verify that scrolling is smooth and that all relevant emails are displayed.

subgoals.description: Select an email from the search results to view its contents.
subgoals.target_element: First email in the search results
subgoals.expected_outcome: The email opens and displays its contents.
subgoals.verification_criteria: Check that the email details are displayed correctly and contain the keyword 'meeting'.

subgoals.description: Go back to the search results after reading the email.
subgoals.expected_outcome: The user is returned to the search result screen.
subgoals.verification_criteria: Verify that the search results screen is displayed again with the previous results intact.

plan.success_criteria: The test is successful if the user can search for emails containing 'meeting', view the results, read an email, and return to the search results, with all functionalities performing as expected.
